Retail Sales Data Pipeline - Day 2 Implementation

Bootcamp Project 1

Objective

The objective of Day 2 was to set up the Azure environment and implement the ingestion layer for the project.

- Azure Resources Created
- Resource Group
- Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2
- Azure SQL Database
- Azure Data Factory
- Azure Key Vault
- Storage Containers Created
  - Bronze : Stores raw ingested data.
  - Silver : Stores cleaned and transformed Parquet datasets.
  - Gold :  Stores business-ready reporting datasets.

SQL Tables Created
- customers
- products
- product_category
- orders
- sales

Linked Services Configured
- Azure SQL Database
- ADLS Gen2
- Azure Key Vault
- REST API

Pipelines Created
- Bronze Ingestion Pipelines
  - SQL to Bronze
  - CSV to Bronze
  - API to SQL Landing

Key Learnings
- Azure resource configuration
- Linked Service setup
- ADF pipeline orchestration
- Bronze layer ingestion process
Secure credential handling using Key Vault
